nts and raising community awareness. Techniques such as banding chicks and preventing disturbances in ground-nesting sites have proven successful. Their resilience, coupled with federal safety measures for related shorebirds, makes their comeback a testament to effective conservation in the face of climate change challenges.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-oystercatchers-were-largely-wiped-out-in-new-england-after-a-10-million-conservation-push-across-16-states-their-numbers-rose-45-along-us-coasts/articleshow/132533043.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-oystercatchers-were-largely-wiped-out-in-new-england-after-a-10-million-conservation-push-across-16-states-their-numbers-rose-45-along-us-coasts/articleshow/132533043.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-21T15:22:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132533074,imgsize-47936.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meet the 73-year-old baby cuddler from Virginia: He has comforted more than 500 premature babies and whispers, 'Grow strong, grow smart, grow kind' before leaving each one]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132532836.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-the-73-year-old-baby-cuddler-from-virginia-he-has-comforted-more-than-500-premature-babies-and-whispers-grow-strong-grow-smart-grow-kind-before-leaving-each-one/articleshow/132532836.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-the-73-year-old-baby-cuddler-from-virginia-he-has-comforted-more-than-500-premature-babies-and-whispers-grow-strong-grow-smart-grow-kind-before-leaving-each-one/articleshow/132532836.cms]]></guid><pubDat